audios.name: 人们的心情伴着节日显...
人们的心情伴着节日显...
她终于拿出了宝贵的一...
小女孩只觉得她看见了...
她不自禁地想要凑上前...
那片迷人的光幕又出现...

texts.content: {"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,16],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"小朋友们穿着漂亮的衣服欢快的跑过"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"他们的脸上洋溢着幸福的笑容"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"与家人吃上一顿美好的年夜饭"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,15],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"人们的心情伴着节日显得十分愉悦"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,15],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"走来了一个穿着褴褛衣服的小女孩"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"她的脚上穿着一双破旧的草鞋"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"露在外面的小脚冻得都瘀紫了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"小女孩哆哆嗦嗦的走在大街上"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"他一只手小心地搭在布袋子上"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"街上的人们渐渐的变得更少了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,15],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"这团烟雾在他迷离的眼中旋绕起来"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,14],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"小女孩只觉得她看见了一片光幕"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"她看到了一团熊熊燃烧的火焰"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,15],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"女孩仿佛置身于这个温暖的火炉旁"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"他不自禁地想要凑上前去取暖"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"颤抖的掏出了一根长长的火柴"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,14],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"他用两只哆嗦的小手举着小火柴"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,15],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"微弱的火光把小女孩的周围照亮了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,16],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"他现在看到的是一个大大的白色餐盘"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"水果上面叠着一个大大的蛋糕"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,14],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"鲜美的奶油快要从上面滴下来了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,16],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"一只肥的流油的烤火鸡摆在了最上面"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,15],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"小女孩的口水还没流到肚子里面去"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,14],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"然而抓到的是一堵又大又冷的墙"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,12],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"火鸡呢小女孩只觉得饿极了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,12],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"他突然想起了他慈祥的父母"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,14],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"这一次他看见了自己魁梧的爸爸"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"你不知道我一个人是多么孤单"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,14],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"爸爸和妈妈微笑着牵起了她的手"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"已经不是那个寒冷的除夕夜了"}

{"styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[1.0,1.0,1.0]}}},"font":{"id":"","path":"D:/Tools/JianyingPro/5.4.0.11246/Resources/Font/SystemFont/zh-hans.ttf"},"range":[0,13],"size":5,"strokes":[{"alpha":1.0,"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"alpha":1.0,"color":[0.0,0.0,0.0]}},"width":0.08}],"useLetterColor":true}],"text":"坐在那冰雪还没有融化的地上"}
